{"tid":1948811,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【武漢肺炎】長江中心39樓職員確診，物管全面消毒各樓層","createTime":"2020-03-29T08:46:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T08:57:26.000Z","uid":278587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"23ab1e1536337acc8b4cc6063e0b1018578b8298","tid":1948811,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T08:46:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20200329/large/1585468824_df13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200329%2Flarge%2F1585468824_df13.jpg&h=4e1e666f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情殺入中環金融區！長江集團中心物業管理有限公司昨（28日）張貼通告，指長江中心39樓租戶的一名職員對病毒檢測呈陽性，長江中心已經加強消毒。<br />\n<br />\n通告表示，確診職員於對上一次進入辦公室時間為本月17日，長江中心物管因應情況已開始徹底消毒，包括確診職員所在及上下3層的辦公樓層、地下大堂、廁所等等。另外，長江中心物管亦呼籲所有租戶如有職員確診，應第一時間向其通知。<br />\n<br />\n記者曾親到長江中心求證，但門外保安不願回應事件，只着記者向公關查詢。《蘋果》目前正向長江集團查詢，等候回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200329/4KXNS234ATKDOVOL4I4UGEZQSM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200329%2F4KXNS234ATKDOVOL4I4UGEZQSM%2F&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJe3s01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=cb32f35a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200329%2F4KXNS234ATKDOVOL4I4UGEZQSM%2F&h=30e177b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200329/4KXNS234ATKDOVOL4I4UGEZQSM/</a>"},{"pid":"c73851b9a263d98c9b91e28a339de7534f5ff489","tid":1948811,"uid":174060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T08:56:18.000Z","msg":"誠哥一定要冇事"},{"pid":"53abbbc2dbe17060681e92dcb0d40c29c35a4db4","tid":1948811,"uid":785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"23ab1e1536337acc8b4cc6063e0b1018578b8298","tid":1948811,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T08:46:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.